OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fin the east throughout Monday evening
OL,7,Fwith late sunny spells. Scattered
OL,8,Fshowers affecting western coasts
OL,9,Finitially, then spreading further
OL,10,Finland overnight and turning locally
OL,11,Fheavy around dawn, perhaps with
OL,12,Fisolated thunder. A cool night for
OL,13,FJune.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTuesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,16,Fblustery showers, with the showers
OL,17,Fpossibly turning heavy in places. An
OL,18,Fisolated chance of thunder in the
OL,19,Fnorth. Temperatures a little below
OL,20,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
