OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FFurther sunshine and showers
OL,7,Fthroughout Wednesday before a spell of
OL,8,Fwet and windy weather moves in for
OL,9,FThursday. Largely cloudy on Friday
OL,10,Fwith patchy rain and drizzle.
